description: A combination of pinball and bingo, this game is fun for the whole family.  You've never played BINGO like this before!  Access your free game card at www.playpinballbingo.com.  Earn points by shooting a ball onto the game card.  Activated BINGO tiles multiply your points.  The first person to get 5 tiles in a row activates a special BINGO bonus round, but with unlimited balls and thousands of potential scenarios, anyone could get the high score and win the game!
